Ngech yadh mzabibu


1  Ruoth Nyasaye nowachona niya,


2  “Wuod dhano,

Ere kaka yadh mzabibu ber moloyo yien mamoko?

Koso ere kaka bade ber moloyo bad yath moro amora?


3  Bende dilos kode gimoro maber?

Koso ding’ad bade mi igur e kor ot mondo ong’awie gik moko?


4  Ooyo, ibole mana e mach mondo ochwake.

To kosebole e majno kamanoo, mi bathe koni gi koni owang’,

kendo kore odong’ korewore,

bende pod dilos kode gimoro malong’o?


5  Kane pok owang’, to onge gima ne inyalo timo kode,

to koro kosewang’, mi kore orewore,

to dobed maonge tich machal nadi?”


6  Kuom mano, an Ruoth Nyasaye awacho niya,

“Kaka yadh mzabibu itong’oe bungu, kendo ichwako,

e kaka abiro kawo jo-Jerusalem


7  mi akum. Kata obedo ni gisetony e mach,

to koro mach biro wang’ogi pep.

Ka asekumogi kamano,

to eka unung’e ni an e Ruoth Nyasaye.


8  Giseweya, omiyo abiro loko pinygi thim.

An Ruoth Nyasaye ema awacho kamano.”

